trans-unit.source: Defines the template of the final step for creating a user account with the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 컨트롤을 사용하여 사용자 계정을 만들기 위한 최종 단계의 템플릿을 정의합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> class is derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep> and used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> 클래스에서 파생 된 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep> 에서 사용 하 고는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: By default the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> step is displayed after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step.
trans-unit.target: 기본적으로는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> 단계 후에 표시 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> 단계입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> step is a required step of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> class.

Gets or sets the type of user interface (UI) to display for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> page of a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> 컨트롤의 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 페이지에 표시할 UI(사용자 인터페이스) 형식을 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete" /> enumeration value for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType" /> enumeration.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property specifies the type of navigation UI to display for the final user account creation step (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step) of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> 속성 탐색 최종 사용자 계정 생성 단계에 표시 하는 UI의 형식을 지정 (의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> 단계)의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase.StepType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to ensure that <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> is always set to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete> value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> 속성 재정의 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase.StepType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 되도록 속성 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> 는 항상으로 설정는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete> 의 값은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType> 열거형입니다.

trans-unit.source: Attempting to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property to a different value will result in an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 설정 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> 속성을 다른 값을 됩니다는 <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>합니다.

trans-unit.source: This property cannot be set by themes or style sheet themes.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성은 테마 또는 스타일시트 테마에 의해 설정될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> and [ASP.NET Themes and Skins](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5df3ebbd-d46c-4502-9406-02f9df4ef2c3).
An attempt was made to set the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType" /> property.
Gets or sets the title to display for the final user account creation step of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 컨트롤의 마지막 사용자 계정 생성 단계에 표시할 제목을 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The title to use for the final user account creation step of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> 컨트롤의 마지막 사용자 계정 생성 단계에 사용할 제목입니다.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property, when set, can be saved automatically to a resource file by using a designer tool.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성의 값으로 설정 하면 디자이너 도구를 사용 하 여 리소스 파일에 자동으로 저장 될 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute> and [Globalization and Localization](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8ef3838e-9d05-4236-9dd0-ceecff9df80d).
